 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Thick-fat:

    This Pokémon takes half as 
  much damage from fire- and ice-type 
  moves.

  Huge-power:

    This Pokémon's Attack is doubled 
  while in battle.

  This bonus does not count as 
  a stat modifier.

  This ability functions identically 
  to pure power.

  Sap-sipper:

    Whenever a grass-type move 
  hits this Pokémon, its Attack 
  rises one stage, negating any 
  other effect on it.


